Two identical 2 frame long .crd files, one with atoimage and rms fit first, and the other without.
cpptraj-ante-MMPBSA.in is used to generate the required inputs for MMPBSA manually (needed if i want to include some explicit waters via a snapshot based distance cutoff)


Cpptraj log files for creation of these two trajectories:

# 05/14/21 10:21:35
parm BRD4-5.prmtop
trajin traj_100ns_stride10.out 1 1001 1000
list
trajout ligand_5_snap1000.crd
exit
go
exit
# 05/14/21 10:22:45
parm BRD4-5.prmtop
trajin traj_100ns_stride10.out 1 1001 1000
autoimage
rms fit first
trajout ligand_5_snap1000_rmsfit_autoimage.crd
go
exit


